{"tid":2084234,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"沙田區議員李世鴻處理違泊及非法擺賣　與人爭執大打出手","createTime":"2020-06-29T07:02:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T06:16:33.000Z","uid":55623,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"16df43731d56005bb5b311dc9e49db0480db9e35","tid":2084234,"uid":55623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T07:02:02.000Z","msg":"勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大圍金禧花園商場對開，今日(29日)下午約1時，沙田區議員李世鴻在上址發現一輛客貨車違例停泊，並疑被人用作擺賣用途。據悉車主為商場地下一間雜貨店店東，李遂上前要求他將車駛走。<br />\n<br />\n期間雙方發生爭執，懷疑有人不忿出手，雙方發生肢體衝突，李的手臂被打傷，有人其後報警。警員聞訊後到場調停，了解事發經過，並向涉事違泊客貨車發出定額罰款通知書，李與涉案雜貨店負責人均報稱受傷，由救護車送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n李世鴻於本月26日透過其Facebook專頁發文，指涉案雜貨舖的負責人將兩輛客貨車，24小時停泊在富嘉花園停車場出入口通道，日間用作擺賣、夜間亦繼續停泊。東網記者正聯絡李世鴻了解事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200629/bkn-20200629133836777-0629_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200629%2Fbkn-20200629133836777-0629_00822_001.html&d=Q4XCoHks6IcJcnuFSE4RTS%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=54d89d2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200629/bkn-20200629133836777-0629_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"200496fa241bf948f711fd38709c7900be0d4730","tid":2084234,"uid":111425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T07:03:56.000Z","msg":"世鴻bb 上年已經比狗打過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8785db3c7b7a07eec87f9eed58f471fd77488613","tid":2084234,"uid":55623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T07:05:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XvVGAKO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXvVGAKO.jpg&h=aaca10af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ee2840d2b